text: Church of St. Mary and Corpus Christi, Down Hatherley. The Church of St Mary & Corpus Christi is a grade II* listed Church of England church in Down Hatherley, Gloucestershire. It was rebuilt to a design by Thomas Fulljames in 1859–60. == References == == External links == Down Hatherly Down Hatherley Category:Borough of Tewkesbury Category:Thomas Fulljames buildings
